   4-23-03 Patch Highlights</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:x-small;">Just some things from the 4-23-03 patch I though some might be interested in <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
- The Lich series no longer conflicts with other DoT effects. This affects Dark Pact, Allure of Death, Call of Bones, Lich, Demi Lich, Arch Lich, Deathly Temptation, Pact of Hate, Ancient: Master of Death and Seduction of Saryrn. <br>
<br>
- Changed the name of the druid spell Fury of Ro to Immolation of Ro to avoid confusion with the focus effect Fury of Ro. </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:xx-small;">And for Karpe specifically I add this ehehehhehe</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:x-small;">- Fixed a bug that would allow PC's to be attacked by PC controlled pets (in non-PvP situations).</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:xx-small;">HEeheh no more pickin' on my MUTTMUTT!</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black size2;font-family:comic sans ms;">- Night's Dark Terror has regained its Scarecrow illusion<br>
<br>
- The cost of the Fuligan Soulstone of Innoruuk has been cut in half. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>ZONES: </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
- Acrylia Caverns, Hollowshade Moor and Grimling Forest have been revamped. We have updated the content in these zones to more accurately represent their design intentions and to address concerns voiced by players. <br>
<br>
- The spires in the Dreadlands are once again sending folks to Luclin. </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:xx-small;">didn't even know that prob was goin' on. . . wonder where peeps were goin'?</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:x-small;"> - Protectors of Growth now actually protect the Plane of Growth again. Beware.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <br>
<br>
  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:xx-small;">Rumor has it this change here made PoG raid plane again not soloable by higher end classes anylonger.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:x-small;"> ** <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Hollow Acrylia Obelisk</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ** <br>
<br>
Do not destroy the Hollow Acrylia Obelisk! Due to the revamp of the Acrylia Caverns, this key will no longer serve its original purpose. We do understand the difficulty of obtaining this key, and we don't want to see that effort lost. We will be looking into a way to allow this key to retain its value, so don't destroy it. <br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>ITEMS:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
- The Ivory Hilted Cleaver can now be used in the secondary slot (for those that can dual-wield). <br>
- The Ornate Broadsword is no longer listed as usable in the secondary slot, since it is Paladin only and can't actually be used there. <br>
- These items can no longer be worn by Frogloks (they were never intended for use by Frogloks): Fright Forged Helm, Mundane Helm, Mundane Shield, Mundane Mask, Dread Forged Shield and Terror Forged Mask </span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
  <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:maroon;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:xx-small;">hope nobody has unwearable gear in the bank now</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :eek --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eek.gif ALT=":eek"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:black;font-family:comic sans ms;font-size:x-small;">- Sharkbone Plated Shoulderpads effect is now &quot;worn&quot; rather than &quot;combat&quot;. <br>
<br>
<br>
** <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Alternate Advancement Abilities</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> ** <br>
<br>
- Made the Servant of Ro AA pet much more potent. <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>MISC:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
- Bind Wounds no longer uses up a bandage for attempting to use the skill when it is not available.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eq-arrow-of-light.com/sigs/asyth.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E6E8fA><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub66.ezboard.com/bthearrowoflightcommons.showUserPublicProfile?gid=asyth>Asyth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Guild Gopher Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 516<br> <font color=#000080>(4/25/03 12:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 4-23-03 Patch Highlights</span><hr size=1> HAar HArr <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I twasn't sure where I wanted to put this eheh thanks Del /wink <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eq-arrow-of-light.com/sigs/asyth.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#A0B0E0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub66.ezboard.com/bthearrowoflightcommons.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aevetare>Aevetare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Arrows own Multiple Personality</span><br>  Posts: 316<br> <font color=#000080>(4/27/03 3:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub66.ezboard.com/fthearrowoflightcommonsfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 4-23-03 Patch Highlights</s